CREATE TABLE payment_data (
    payment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    payment_date DATE,
    customer_id INT,
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  payment_id INT,
  order_date DATE,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    quantity INT
);
